  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the aim of the study is to evaluate the efficiency of the therapy with negative pression
      (TPN) and instillation in the debridement of chronic wound
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      it is an observation study with only the aim to evaluate the percentage of fibrin before and
      after the specific treatment of TPN
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
